What you need to know:

The big-serving 22nd seed secured her first Grand Slam final appearance on her fifth match point against the Czech 25th seed in front of thousands of fans allowed back on Rod Laver ArenaThe warm conditions were expected to suit Brady and she started fast with an early break, but Muchova settled her nerves and clawed back into the contestA nervous Brady was forced to fend off three break points before finally booking a spot in her maiden Grand Slam final on her fifth match point, falling to the ground in euphoria